  "title": "Junior Sales Engineer / Sales Executive (Engineering) | Mandai | Up to $4,000 + Comm + AWS + VB",
  "description": "<h2>Duties and Responsibilities</h2><ul><li><p>Conduct island-wide sales activities across Singapore, including client visits and follow-ups</p></li><li><p>Promote and sell engineering products and solutions to customers</p></li><li><p>Operate under a commission-based sales structure aligned with performance targets</p></li><li><p>Review contracts and commercial terms received from customers and provide recommendations or advice to top management</p></li><li><p>Coordinate with management on contract risks, payment terms, and execution matters</p></li><li><p>Actively follow up and chase outstanding payments from customers</p></li><li><p>Handle and resolve payment disputes professionally, coordinating with customers and internal teams</p></li><li><p>Maintain ongoing relationships with clients to support repeat business and long-term accounts</p></li><li><p>Provide basic sales updates and status reports to management</p></li></ul><h2>Required Qualifications and Attributes</h2><ul><li><p>Diploma or Degree in Engineering or related discipline preferred</p></li><li><p>Relevant experience in sales, technical sales, or engineering-related roles</p></li><li><p>Comfortable with island-wide travel for work</p></li><li><p>Experience handling contracts, payment follow-ups, and customer coordination</p></li><li><p>Strong communication, negotiation, and follow-up skills</p></li><li><p>Able to work independently with minimal supervision</p></li><li><p>Ability to communicate with regional stakeholders may be beneficial for work coordination.</p></li></ul><h2>Working Hours / Working Days</h2><ul><li><p>Monday to Friday</p></li><li><p>Standard office hours (flexibility required based on client needs)<br /></p><p>EA License No: 23C1703</p><p>EA Personnel No: R1762582</p><p>EA Personnel Name: Wong Choo Sian, Jabez</p></li></ul>",
